						<a class="post_more_title" href="https://lithub.com/1979s-the-book-store-book-documents-a-lost-borough-of-booksellers/">
				<h7 style="display:block;">1979’s <em>The Book-Store Book</em> documents a lost borough of booksellers.</h7>
			</a>
			In 1979, President Jimmy Carter established the Department of Education and was attacked by a rabbit. In 1979, New York City...			</div>
